    "Figures 5b, 5d, 5f, 5h, 5j, 5l, 5n, and 5p represents the energy distribution of human-and ChatGPT-generated content in relation to the EBM prediction.",
    "It is important to highlight that misclassifications were observed for certain samples across different datasets, which introduces the possibility of reverse perturbed energies for both label options (0 or 1).",
    "Consequently, confusion matrices for both label 0 and label 1, with distinct true positives (TP), true negatives (TN), false positives (FP), and false negatives (FN), are depicted in Figures 5b, 5f, 5h, 5j, 5l, 5n, and 5p.",
